---
import I18n from './I18n.astro';
---

<section class="section reveal" id="about">
  <div class="section-label">
    <I18n en="About" zh="关于我" />
  </div>
  <h2 class="section-title">
    <I18n
      en="From monoliths to microservices to data platforms."
      zh="从单体到微服务，再到数据平台。"
    />
  </h2>
  <p>
    <I18n
      en="Fourteen years as a programmer at internet companies—backend and platform lead across mobile apps, management systems, and SaaS; high-traffic systems and company-wide data platforms."
      zh="十四年程序员，主要在互联网企业做后端和平台负责人——APP、各类管理系统与企业 SaaS 都做过，写过核心链路和高并发系统，也搭过公司级数仓。"
    />
  </p>
  <p>
    <I18n
      en="I focus on evolvable architecture and engineering maturity—clear domain boundaries, end-to-end observability, and standardized release pipelines that keep delivery sustainable and technical debt manageable at scale."
      zh="注重系统的可演进性与工程化建设：领域边界清晰、全链路可观测、发布灰度可回滚，保障业务快速迭代下的可持续交付与技术债可控。"
    />
  </p>
  <p>
    <I18n
      en="Recent focus: enterprise architecture, refactors, microservices with Spring Cloud, and data pipelines shared across teams."
      zh="最近几年：企业内部架构、项目重构、Spring Cloud 微服务，以及跨团队共用的数据链路。"
    />
  </p>
  <p>
    <I18n
      en="I've also run ops solo on Alibaba Cloud and Tencent Cloud—Linux scripts, CI/CD, and getting things live."
      zh="也曾一个人扛运维：阿里云、腾讯云，写脚本、跑 CI/CD、负责上线。"
    />
  </p>
</section>
